sld 2000 sld 2000 the latest draft of the proposal for continued running of sld in the 21st century is now ready this proposal will be presented to the slac epac in early september the full extension request is a series of four documents the sld request for extension sld_request ps a document describing the current slc slc_performance ps an slc upgrades proposal slc_upgrades ps a document describing the benefits to nlc nlc_benefits ps the documents can also be downloaded as a single compressed archive in two format sld_extension tar gz unix sld_extension zip ibm windows nt please send comments suggestions etc to the official editor of the document john jaros wednesday november 14 2001
